Enter our competition for the chance to win a trip to Arctic Sweden worth £3,000
The lucky winners will be be flown to Bjorkliden (above) in northern Sweden for a three-night adventure Photo: CHAD BLAKLEY	10:53AM GMT 14 Nov 2013
