The trip will run from February 17-20 and will include flights and transfers to and from Bjorkliden with a traditional Swedish Fika (afternoon tea) on arrival; accommodation on a half board basis; a "Lights over Lapland" photography trip with Chad Blakley and a Låkta Aurora adventure trip to the highest mountain lodge in the region. The prize will also include hire of specialist arctic clothing. Off the Map Travel Off the Map Travel (offthemaptravel.co.uk) is a soft adventure travel company that specialises in trips to view the aurora borealis. The company has brought together a group of travel experts who are passionate about adventure and who specialise in bespoke trips to exceptional destinations such as Bjorkliden - off the regular travel routes, but places with a luxurious touch. How to enter Simply fill in the form below. Entries should be submitted my midnight on Friday December 13, 2013. Click here for full terms and conditions. Online Form - Win a northern lights holiday worth £3,000
